  },
  {
    "row": 11,
    "rowsha": "VSjGvyvE8DoGpI8MlVxNYcbK5Nlr+AeYdszHmOX1iUM=",
    "originContent": "> **‼️ Windows Defender False Positive** (literally no idea why or where this came from)",
    "translatedContent": "> **‼️ Windows Defenderの誤検知**（なぜこれが発生しているのか全く不明です）"
  },
  {
    "row": 12,
    "rowsha": "YrZ+H2hbf+9RECAF3d0nd0vj/uOMQpZcU6qwNdC2siE=",
    "originContent": ">",
    "translatedContent": ">"
  },
  {
    "row": 13,
    "rowsha": "cJfzZMvWPeFYTnD55LTpPJLftACJywImjRDaZvZ/9OU=",
    "originContent": "> The Windows executable of this program is frequently being flagged as **`Trojan:Script/Wacatac.B!ml`** by Windows Defender and other AV. This is a **false positive**.",
    "translatedContent": "> このプログラムのWindows実行ファイルは、Windows Defenderや他のアンチウイルスによって頻繁に **`Trojan:Script/Wacatac.B!ml`** として検出されます。これは**誤検知**です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 14,
    "rowsha": "YrZ+H2hbf+9RECAF3d0nd0vj/uOMQpZcU6qwNdC2siE=",
    "originContent": ">",
    "translatedContent": ">"
  },
  {
    "row": 15,
    "rowsha": "uIimVJT5rdQjh4CBOPktD3ZvepT/Id/McqmHRBgYr0w=",
    "originContent": "> **Why is this happening?**",
    "translatedContent": "> **なぜこれが起こるのか？**"
  },
  {
    "row": 16,
    "rowsha": "wctLVTpX7JuPh/gw0rjTulyEaNh5iqaKFK5ilQ1QvYk=",
    "originContent": "> The `!ml` in the detection name means it was flagged by a Machine Learning model, not a human. Because this is an unsigned, open-source scraper tool that makes many internet requests, the automated system incorrectly flags it as suspicious. This is a common issue for many Go and Rust-based command-line tools.",
    "translatedContent": "> 検出名の `!ml` は、これは人間ではなく機械学習モデルによってフラグ付けされたことを意味します。このプログラムは署名されていないオープンソースのスクレイパーツールで、多数のインターネットリクエストを行うため、自動システムが誤って疑わしいものとして検出しています。これはGoやRustベースの多くのコマンドラインツールでよくある問題です。"
  },
  {
    "row": 17,
    "rowsha": "YrZ+H2hbf+9RECAF3d0nd0vj/uOMQpZcU6qwNdC2siE=",
    "originContent": ">",
    "translatedContent": ">"
  },
  {
    "row": 18,
    "rowsha": "z8ogJjEF5v7xs4jJzO9B/jG1W2FfFXWwOMfVYqm4DJw=",
    "originContent": "> **Recommended Solution - Install via Go (should hopefully bypass AV issues):**",
    "translatedContent": "> **推奨される解決策 - Go経由でインストール（おそらくAV問題を回避可能）：**"
  },
  {
    "row": 19,
    "rowsha": "wdkEOeFso6tqiT11qRgwNFig8+xjxbk3wJKCvpYihdM=",
    "originContent": "> ```bash",
    "translatedContent": "> ```bash"
  },
  {
    "row": 20,
    "rowsha": "z+QVTiwlP3J6e2FcF6fqGvfdfdxAKnkAwanzkxuMNZk=",
    "originContent": "> go install github.com/agnosto/fansly-scraper/cmd/fansly-scraper@latest",
    "translatedContent": "> go install github.com/agnosto/fansly-scraper/cmd/fansly-scraper@latest"
  },
  {
    "row": 21,
    "rowsha": "MSWTuK53TAylT2dLwAgGiANzYPowZK3H1tOGCQeahfM=",
    "originContent": "> ```",
    "translatedContent": "> ```"
